<% const pageTitle = "Shipping & Delivery Policy – VK Training Consultency"; %>
<%- include('partials/head') %>
<%- include('partials/navbar') %>

<main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-2">Shipping &amp; Delivery Policy</h1>
  <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-10">Last updated: 25 April 2026</p>

  <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none space-y-8 text-slate-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">1. Digital-Only Products</h2>
      <p>VK Training Consultency exclusively offers digital educational content (video courses, study materials, and related resources). <strong>No physical goods are shipped.</strong> There are no shipping charges applied to any purchase.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">2. Instant Digital Delivery</h2>
      <p>Upon successful payment confirmation from Razorpay, access to your purchased course(s) is granted <strong>immediately and automatically</strong> within your student dashboard. You will also receive a purchase confirmation email.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">3. Access Period</h2>
      <p>Unless otherwise stated on the course page, access to purchased courses is granted for the lifetime of your active account. We reserve the right to retire course content with at least 30 days' notice.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">4. Delayed Access</h2>
      <p>In rare cases of technical issues, course access may be delayed. If you do not see your purchased course in your dashboard within 30 minutes of a successful payment, please contact our support team with your payment transaction ID.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">5. System Requirements</h2>
      <p>To access course content you need a stable internet connection and a modern browser (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, or Edge). Video content is streamed and is not available for offline download.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">6. Contact</h2>
      <p>For delivery-related queries:<br />
      <strong>VK Training Consultency</strong><br />
      Email: <a href="mailto:support@vktraining.in" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">support@vktraining.in</a></p>
    </section>

  </div>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
